    <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-8">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
                TopClanker aggregates scores from established, peer-reviewed benchmarks published by the AI research community.
                We don't make up numbers. Every score links back to published results.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Think of it like Rotten Tomatoes for AI:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600 mr-2">🎯 Benchmark Score</span>
